<Weakness xmlns="http://cwe.mitre.org/cwe-7" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" ID="696" Name="Incorrect Behavior Order" Abstraction="Class" Structure="Simple" Status="Incomplete">
         <Description>The product performs multiple related behaviors, but the behaviors are performed in the wrong order in ways that may produce resultant weaknesses.</Description>
         <Related_Weaknesses>
